document.topic_text: Al Malaikah Host 3rd Annual Golf Tournament Benefiting Shriners… Pasadena, California (PRWEB) August 17, 2016 The Al Malaikah Shrine Club is scheduled to hold its 3rd annual Golf Tournament Saturday, Sept. 23 at Brookside Golf and Country Club, with check-in starting at 8 a.m. and the tournament start scheduled for 9 a.m. The annual event raises money to help support the Shriners Hospitals for Children – Los Angeles. The single player fee is $125 per golfer, which includes golf, cart and lunch. Sponsorhip Opportutnites rage from Bronze Sponsor $500 to Platinum Sponsor $5,000. For more information and an application visist almalaikahgolf.com or call Shriners Hospitals for Children – Los Angeles 213-368-3316 Shriners Hospitals for Children® – Los Angeles is a specialty…
